Paul Page (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Paul_Page_(actor) 0 Paul Page (May 13, 1903 in Birmingham, Alabama – April 28, 1974), was an American film actor. Born Campbell U. Hicks, he was the son of Robert C. Hicks and Laura Conant Hicks.Page attended Baltimore Polytechnic Institute and graduated from St. John's College in Annapolis with a degree in engineering.On July 10, 1929, he married Ethel Allis.
